snippet.title: Ara: History Untold - Developer Game Overview | Xbox & Bethesda Games Showcase 2022
snippet.description:
Michelle Menard and Dan Baker, the Design Director and Founder of Oxide Games, provide more details about their new alternate-history grand strategy game Ara: History Untold.
